{"words":[{"word":"observatory","count":3},{"word":"lahai-roi","count":3},{"word":"sephira","count":2},{"word":"everything","count":2},{"word":"afraid","count":2},{"word":"help","count":2},{"word":"feel","count":2},{"word":"roya","count":1},{"word":"exoswarm","count":1},{"word":"architecture","count":1},{"word":"culture","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"protected","count":1},{"word":"void","count":1},{"word":"storm","count":1},{"word":"erases","count":1},{"word":"devours","count":1},{"word":"gone","count":1},{"word":"spacetrek","count":1},{"word":"surveys","count":1},{"word":"records","count":1},{"word":"history","count":1},{"word":"land","count":1},{"word":"remembered","count":1},{"word":"face","count":1},{"word":"danger","count":1},{"word":"contribution","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"watch","count":1},{"word":"everyone","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"disappearing","count":1},{"word":"atonement","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"eventually","count":1},{"word":"view","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"phase","count":1},{"word":"toughest","count":1},{"word":"worried","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"rest","count":1},{"word":"breeze","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"whenever","count":1},{"word":"others","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"visit","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"set","count":1},{"word":"little","count":1},{"word":"tent","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"helped","count":1},{"word":"homesickness","count":1},{"word":"became","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"precious","count":1},{"word":"especially","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"dwell","count":1},{"word":"sad","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"today","count":1},{"word":"placed","count":1},{"word":"plenty","count":1},{"word":"supply","count":1},{"word":"chests","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"researcher","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"top","count":1},{"word":"contributor","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"asked","count":1},{"word":"talkie","count":1},{"word":"bring","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"unlock","count":1},{"word":"open","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Sephira. The Roya. The Exoswarm. Our architecture and culture… must be protected.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"The Void Storm… erases. Devours. Everything... gone.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Spacetrek Observatory... surveys. Records. Our history. The land of Lahai-Roi... remembered.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Face. Danger. I... make contribution.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"I stay... in Observatory. Watch over... you. Everyone. Lahai-Roi.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Not afraid. Our people… Lahai-Roi… disappearing. That... I'm afraid.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Sephira. Help me. Your atonement. You'll understand… eventually.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Look at this view. All thanks to you.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"One last phase, and the toughest one. But... not worried.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Take a rest. Feel the breeze.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Haha, you could say that. Whenever the others came to visit, they'd always set up this little tent for me, so I'd feel at home.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Overwatch Phase","quest_id":176000007},{"text":"Back then, I couldn't tell them how much it helped my homesickness. It became really precious, especially after everything that happened...","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Overwatch Phase","quest_id":176000007},{"text":"But let's not dwell on sad things today! We've placed plenty of supply chests all around the Observatory, enough for every researcher to find what they need.","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Overwatch Phase","quest_id":176000007},{"text":"And you, as our top contributor, can help yourself to any of them! I even asked Talkie to bring some just for you. Here, I'll unlock them. You can open them now!","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Overwatch Phase","quest_id":176000007},{"text":"Come on!","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Overwatch Phase","quest_id":176000007}]}